{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"P4Bc5OxNsCoXxvn9RwGkb","title":"伪造信息","desc":"","updated":1651066038650,"created":1644897839290,"custom":{},"fname":"censorship.disinformation","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"d010fa0ed35bb78b37f24a1685b83127","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.disinformation","id":"P4Bc5OxNsCoXxvn9RwGkb","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"censorship.censors","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":41,"offset":41},"end":{"line":2,"column":63,"offset":63},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"censorship.censors"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.disinformation","id":"P4Bc5OxNsCoXxvn9RwGkb","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"fiftycentparty","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":68,"offset":914},"end":{"line":20,"column":86,"offset":932},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"fiftycentparty"}},{"from":{"fname":"censorship.censorship2","id":"A8qE6ccsmj4Kz7VD3GjhW","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":34,"offset":140},"end":{"line":7,"column":63,"offset":169},"indent":[]},"value":"censorship.disinformation"}],"anchors":{"自创假新闻":{"type":"header","text":"自创假新闻","value":"自创假新闻","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"内容篡改":{"type":"header","text":"内容篡改","value":"内容篡改","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"伪造信息disinformation和错误信息misinformation的差别":{"type":"header","text":"伪造信息（Disinformation）和错误信息（Misinformation）的差别","value":"伪造信息disinformation和错误信息misinformation的差别","line":22,"column":0,"depth":2},"参考资料":{"type":"header","text":"参考资料","value":"参考资料","line":29,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["gamg0j2oolmmljp44w2iq9s"],"parent":"qAItL5nac0TIpD7Uv7eB5","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"伪造信息\">伪造信息<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#伪造信息\"></a></h1>\n<p>因为防火长城，中国的绝大多数用户在不能翻墙的情况下只能消费本土创造的内容。这就为<a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/8A0FRLzxU7KhBEgTAFqDn\">审查者</a>创造了一个最便利的机会来编造假信息来误导受众，进而增强了审查的效果。</p>\n<h2 id=\"自创假新闻\">自创假新闻<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#自创假新闻\"></a></h2>\n<p>一个知名的案例是在2021年Covid-19 病毒流行阶段，中国官方媒体上出现了一个“知名”的<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6\">瑞士专家</a> \"Wilson Edwards\" 对Covid-19 病毒发表的观点，多数是赞成中国的防疫政策、国产疫苗或反对调查病毒起源。瑞士政府为此专门调查并经驻北京大使馆<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/669487.html\">发表声明</a>，证实此人根本不存在。</p>\n<p>另一个知名的案例是俄罗斯官方媒体推荐一个法国“记者”的视频，用来指控乌克兰军队“屠杀”顿巴斯地区的居民。后经过媒体和民间调查这位记者根本没有可能在当时进入顿巴斯采访拍摄，而且对其“报道”的居民死亡数字（13000），完全是<a href=\"https://twitter.com/angrytoad2046/status/1500096162375913473\">拼接而成</a>。但是因为俄国官方的推荐，中国官方媒体则毫无迟疑地配合这种宣传。</p>\n<h2 id=\"内容篡改\">内容篡改<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#内容篡改\"></a></h2>\n<p>A History of the Future in 100 Objects，中文版审查掉了 9 个故事，书名直接改成《给 91件未来事物写历史》。</p>\n<h2 id=\"伪造信息disinformation和错误信息misinformation的差别\">伪造信息（Disinformation）和错误信息（Misinformation）的差别<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#伪造信息disinformation和错误信息misinformation的差别\"></a></h2>\n<p>伪造信息是有意为之，而错误信息则常常来自于对来源缺乏查验。对审查者来说，伪造信息的目的是利用信息受众对信息的渴求有意制造假信息并在社交媒体上传播，可以形成媒姆(Meme)效应，有效干扰用户对其他信息的获取。</p>\n<p>阴谋论也成为官方的雇佣手段，在一些灾难（例如“MU5735航班坠毁” ）发生时，大量的五毛/水军会出现在社交媒体，例如机器人账号或各种<a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">fiftycentparty (Private)</a>帐号发出类似的信息“美国军方故意控制MU5735航班坠毁”<a id=\"fnref-1\" class=\"fnref\" href=\"#fn-1\">1</a>，污染用户的时间线。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考资料\">参考资料<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#参考资料\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/firstdraftnews/status/1498086037083475968\">Difference between MISinformation and DISinformation</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/gamg0j2oolmmljp44w2iq9s\">驻外大使的推特</a></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"footnotes\">Footnotes<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#footnotes\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><span id=\"fn-1\" style=\"width: 0; height: 0;\"></span><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/678749.html\">【五毛话术】“美国军方故意控制MU5735航班坠毁”、“波音公司应全球停飞”</a><a class=\"fn\" href=\"#fnref-1\">˄</a></p></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/A8qE6ccsmj4Kz7VD3GjhW\">Censorship2</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","title":"墙国地图","desc":"","updated":1646712715590,"created":1644382378522,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"02c3c0c9e63ff90b668e6396d3f28d2a","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"underlying","alias":"实现方法","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":3,"offset":213},"end":{"line":12,"column":22,"offset":232},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"underlying"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"underlying","alias":"开源工具","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":3,"offset":382},"end":{"line":15,"column":24,"offset":403},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"underlying"}}],"anchors":{"如何使用审查地图":{"type":"header","text":"如何使用审查地图","value":"如何使用审查地图","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["vJRHPlmEzy8aoLmJq2EoS","qAItL5nac0TIpD7Uv7eB5","lFNqSJwuUdJJM9syQlMLP","4s98naE7Vp8rLwaBGAoRU","9mBvciCymZgzfdO2sVbde","EW05BFjl1ivR37Yv0wBIM","rTDV3gbrzSF4qbFVVLaPk"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n![](/assets/images/logo.png)\n\n墙国地图是社群共同贡献和维护的开源项目，目的是保存中国审查体系的来龙去脉，审查影响到的方方面面，人们的反制以及各种相关联的事件。\n\n因为采用了一种开放设计的机制，这个地图的版本将不断迭代并随时向贡献者发放特别的激励，所以你也可以加入并成为其中的一部分。\n\n## 如何使用审查地图\n\n审查地图是一个开源项目，你可以按图索骥，也可以补充完善，或者与更多人分享。\n\n- [[实现方法|underlying]]     \n- [源代码](https://github.com/China-Digital-Times-CDT/censorshipgraph)\n- [讨论](https://github.com/China-Digital-Times-CDT/censorshipgraph/issues)\n- [[开源工具 | underlying]]\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":